OL,3,CPeople leaving flowers at crash scene
OL,4,C'at risk of being hit'
OL,6,FPeople mourning the death of a man who
OL,7,Fwas hit by a car are putting
OL,8,Fthemselves at risk by laying flowers
OL,9,Fat the scene, police have said.
OL,11,FThe 19-year-old was walking on the A64
OL,12,Fbetween Grimston Bar and the Hopgrove
OL,13,FRoundabout, near York, when he
OL,14,Fsuffered fatal injuries in the crash
OL,15,Fon Saturday night.
OL,17,FNorth Yorkshire Police said people
OL,18,Fwanting to pay tribute were putting
OL,19,Fthemselves and other road users at
OL,20,Frisk.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
