OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774541484
OL,3,CPeople leaving flowers at crash scene
OL,4,C'at risk of being hit'
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We have received
OL,7,Freports from members of the public
OL,8,Fthat people stopping on the roadside
OL,9,Fto leave flowers, cards and messages
OL,10,Fwere placing themselves at risk of
OL,11,Fbeing struck by passing vehicles."
OL,13,FPeople wanting to leave flowers have
OL,14,Fbeen asked to use another location
OL,15,Funderneath the A64 on Murton Way.
OL,17,FThe investigation into the crash is
OL,18,Fcontinuing and witnesses are being
OL,19,Fasked to come forward.
